{"tid":45394,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"一齊分享下2016睇過啲咩戲","createTime":"2016-12-19T02:45:00.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-22T08:41:06.000Z","uid":12973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f3e7e8cdd7bc8e6825b402abd09a1e8d5087f3fe","tid":45394,"uid":12973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:45:00.000Z","msg":"1. The Revenant<br />\nLeonardo DiCaprio 拋低過往形象，一個人carry哂成套戲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. Carol<br />\nRooney Mara 做女友每日生活點過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. Spotlight<br />\n狠狠痛擊耶撚既一套戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n4. Room<br />\n其實我覺得最後有啲爛尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n5. 暗色天堂<br />\n呢套真係正，講牧師違反自己既教條<br />\n張學友林嘉欣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n6. Civil War 3<br />\n對於平時唔睇英雄片既我，都幾緊湊冇乜冷場<br />\n<br />\n7. 喪屍末日戰<br />\nHero 係入型入格既毒撚，有村架純bb豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n8. 把她帶回家<br />\n印度戲既歌係幾好聽，但拉到套戲好長太煽情<br />\n<br />\n9. Now You See Me 2<br />\n主角威能，bugs多到暈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n10. 寒戰2<br />\n主角威能 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n11. 三人行<br />\n杜sir啲鏡頭仲係好靚（除左槍戰）<br />\n劇情都幾特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n12. 點五步<br />\n好熱血好貼地值得支持既本地創作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n13. 屍殺列車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n14. 湄公河行動<br />\n有人送戲飛先睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，奶共<br />\n<br />\n15. 哭聲<br />\n集懸疑驚嚇推理於一身既電影<br />\n臨尾真係寒都心埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n16. 七月與安生<br />\n兩個主角性格立體，好入心既成長故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時我自己係七月，有時係安生<br />\n周冬雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n17. Hacksaw Ridge<br />\n好睇only"},{"pid":"7281d7fc65a51c2944f9cd1a6459ba4d1776d822","tid":45394,"uid":60682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T02:56:24.000Z","msg":"樹大招風<br />\n因為對舊案有興趣而睇<br />\n<br />\n肌智同學會<br />\n<br />\n你的名字<br />\n<br />\n怪獸與他們的產地<br />\n<br />\n無咩時間就到睇戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d70e1031b41650ad76788cb38e727b3e5f7df59","tid":45394,"uid":51446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T08:31:59.000Z","msg":"Boyhood"},{"pid":"d14a117a738ee5344aef4f4deca00d80d6db2c20","tid":45394,"uid":66045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T08:39:02.000Z","msg":"睇左太多戲唔記得<br />\n但最深刻覺得好睇係<br />\nNerve <br />\n柏鳥小姐<br />\n怪獸<br />\n<br />\n你的名仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能我膚淺睇唔明"},{"pid":"a6d8e70481d4d19e37df89bf5dc2fc6831404782","tid":45394,"uid":14474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T08:40:06.000Z","msg":"Revenant<br />\nDeadpool<br />\nSpotlight<br />\nZootopia <br />\n十年 <br />\n復仇者3<br />\n屍殺列車<br />\n柏麗小姐 <br />\n鑽油台果套<br />\nFantastic beast"},{"pid":"c48e8294206974a82738fb66daa3e8d477020636","tid":45394,"uid":13961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T08:41:06.000Z","msg":"有無得睇上過乜戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}